83
01:22:44,094 --> 01:22:46,960
Then the mother should sleep with the child

84
01:22:47,040 --> 01:22:49,973
and the father should sleep in another room.

85
01:22:50,580 --> 01:22:52,980
Mother should never leave the child.

86
01:22:55,260 --> 01:22:59,527
Moreover, I would advise you that now you have children,

87
01:22:59,607 --> 01:23:04,007
don’t get too much involved with your children. That’s a dangerous

88
01:23:04,087 --> 01:23:10,000
thing. This is another phase: first, they get involved with the wives or husbands,

89
01:23:10,080 --> 01:23:13,141
then they get involved with the children.

90
01:23:13,221 --> 01:23:19,500
If you get involved with the children, then again, you have to restart many things.

91
01:23:19,580 --> 01:23:21,113
So, don’t get involved.

92
01:23:21,880 --> 01:23:27,610
You have to just do the work like a trustee of the child, just a trustee

93
01:23:27,690 --> 01:23:31,355
of the child. But don’t get involved with the child.

94
01:23:32,035 --> 01:23:34,964
That is my job. You have to leave it to Me.

95
01:23:35,044 --> 01:23:38,357
So, don’t get too much involved with the children.

96
01:23:38,437 --> 01:23:43,885
I find people who got children, you see, are going now wrtiting literature on it.

97
01:23:43,965 --> 01:23:45,231
Don’t do like that.

98
01:23:46,049 --> 01:23:50,515
I’ve already given instructions what is to be done about the child.

99
01:23:50,595 --> 01:23:53,061
But the children are mine, not yours.

100
01:23:53,141 --> 01:23:58,340
So, you just don’t get involved into them because that’s a temptation for you.

101
01:23:58,420 --> 01:24:02,686
Too much involvement in the children is the sign of degradation.

102
01:24:03,530 --> 01:24:07,684
It’s only a responsibility to look after it. That’s all.

103
01:24:09,500 --> 01:24:16,499
So, tell them.And mother must be with children, must be with children.

104
01:25:08,360 --> 01:25:10,281
She should sleep with them;

105
01:25:10,361 --> 01:25:14,294
she should look after them till they are five years of age.

106
01:25:19,110 --> 01:25:23,976
If she has to go out, then she must know that she has to carry the child.

107
01:25:24,460 --> 01:25:27,600
She cannot leave children. That’s not good.

108
01:25:27,680 --> 01:25:33,213
She should never leave the child before they are five years of age, whatever it is.

109
01:25:43,765 --> 01:25:46,631
Because you should know that till that age,

110
01:25:46,711 --> 01:25:50,430
