111
01:25:51,065 --> 01:25:55,331
You see, at an old age, say, somebody is ninety and ninety-five,

112
01:25:55,411 --> 01:25:57,344
there is not much difference.

113
01:26:08,397 --> 01:26:12,330
And at that time, the sense of security must be maintained.

114
01:26:12,410 --> 01:26:13,743
That, one has to do!

115
01:26:21,000 --> 01:26:26,440
So, if the husband has to do something else or if he has to go out or anything,

116
01:26:26,520 --> 01:26:28,593
