118
01:26:34,340 --> 01:26:36,606
that’s her duty, she has to do it!

119
01:26:41,730 --> 01:26:46,541
And of course, the husband must help her, must do whatever is needed.

120
01:26:46,621 --> 01:26:52,345
But here the question is of

121
