122
01:26:54,914 --> 01:26:57,780
Now, at this time, the mother is important.

123
01:26:57,860 --> 01:27:01,460
She has to look after the child, that’s her first job.

124
01:27:01,540 --> 01:27:05,340
And at time, the husband’s job becomes a secondary thing.

125
01:27:05,420 --> 01:27:07,440
But hers is the first job.

126
01:27:07,520 --> 01:27:11,470
And later on, then,

127
01:27:11,550 --> 01:27:18,530
it again shifts because husband’s

128
01:27:18,610 --> 01:27:24,820
