133
01:27:42,421 --> 01:27:46,421
Because completely the mothers forget about the whole world.

134
01:27:46,501 --> 01:27:51,351
You’ll be surprised, till my younger daughter was five years of age,

135
01:27:51,431 --> 01:27:54,031
