138
01:28:44,550 --> 01:28:48,730
Because that pays more money or gives you artificial powers.

139
01:28:52,630 --> 01:28:57,230
You must know the greatest power in this world is that of the mother.

140
01:29:00,078 --> 01:29:05,411
